      <title>为什么内华达州是 2024 年大选最难以预测的摇摆州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/nevada-polls-vary-most-of-key-states-in-trump-biden-presidential-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统大选的所有战场州中，没有哪个州比内华达州更让拜登和特朗普感到困惑了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/nevada-polls-vary-most-of-key-states-in-trump-biden-presidential-race</guid>
