      <title>首尔称朝鲜垃圾气球中发现寄生虫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/parasites-were-found-in-north-korea-s-trash-balloons-seoul-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔当局称，在朝鲜飘入韩国的载有垃圾的气球中发现了与粪便有关的寄生虫，还有内衣、领带和袜子等衣物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/parasites-were-found-in-north-korea-s-trash-balloons-seoul-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 08:53:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北马其顿任命新政府或使与欧盟关系紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/north-macedonia-appoints-government-that-may-strain-ties-with-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北马其顿议会支持民族主义者领导的政府，这可能会恶化与欧盟的关系，并进一步阻碍这个巴尔干国家加入欧盟的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/north-macedonia-appoints-government-that-may-strain-ties-with-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 07:09:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>距离大选不到一周，勒庞领导的极右翼势力持续崛起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/le-pen-s-far-right-keeps-rising-less-than-a-week-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的民意调查显示，在周日法国提前立法选举首轮投票之前，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟取得了进一步的发展，而法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙面临与反对派政府分享权力的可能性越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/le-pen-s-far-right-keeps-rising-less-than-a-week-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 07:00:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称 6 月 17 日海上冲突是中国“蓄意行为”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/philippines-says-june-17-sea-clash-a-deliberate-act-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾称，上周在有争议的南海与中国发生的冲突导致一名菲律宾士兵失去一根手指，这是北京的“故意行为”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/philippines-says-june-17-sea-clash-a-deliberate-act-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 06:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨称南非政府必须加快改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/south-africa-s-government-must-accelerate-reform-ramaphosa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，南非新政府必须加快改革步伐，以改善商业环境并吸引投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/south-africa-s-government-must-accelerate-reform-ramaphosa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 06:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>下一任印尼领导人表示将对支出协议保持克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/prabowo-budgets-4-3-billion-for-free-meals-to-keep-deficit-cap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼候任总统普拉博沃·苏比安托与即将离任的政府达成协议，为学校免费膳食计划拨款 71 万亿卢比（43 亿美元），此举不会超出预算赤字上限，并旨在缓解市场对扩张性支出的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/prabowo-budgets-4-3-billion-for-free-meals-to-keep-deficit-cap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:55:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港最高法院审理黎智英上诉案 审查日益严厉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/hong-kong-top-court-hears-jimmy-lai-appeal-as-scrutiny-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一批外籍法官相继离职后，香港司法系统再度受到审视，香港最高法院开始首次审理前媒体大亨黎智英在 2019 年支持民主的抗议活动中所扮演的角色一案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/hong-kong-top-court-hears-jimmy-lai-appeal-as-scrutiny-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在新议会中饱受争议的政策议程面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/parts-of-modi-s-agenda-face-risk-in-india-s-fractured-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党十年来首次未能赢得议会绝对多数席位，这使其庞大的国内议程陷入危险，迫使该党不得不与多个政党联盟合作，并与扩大的反对党席位展开斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/parts-of-modi-s-agenda-face-risk-in-india-s-fractured-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克领导的保守党担心博彩丑闻可能扩大并埋葬他们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/rishi-sunak-s-tories-fear-betting-scandal-may-expand-and-bury-them</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在英国大选中避免惨败的机会进一步减小，因为有消息称首相的几位亲密助手对投票日期进行了押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/rishi-sunak-s-tories-fear-betting-scandal-may-expand-and-bury-them</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
